<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>11111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里基八岁了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很聪明，并且有着大大的梦想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>曾经，他想做消防员。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他总是在头上戴头盔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还试着用胶皮管练习喷水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而事实上他也喝了很多水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一段时间，他还对车感兴趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想做一名赛车手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在沿着车道跑的时候他用嘴发出引擎的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他可以说出每一辆经过的车的型号。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那段时间里，他总是坐在车的副驾驶的位置上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为他想学习如何开车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，里基对他的父亲说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸，我长大后想做北极探险家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的爸爸并不吃惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毕竟，里基曾经想过做消防员、赛车手、超人、画家，甚至芭蕾舞演员。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可以，里基，但是你要知道，北极是很冷的。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里基想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“住在北极会很辛苦吗？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，你要忍受严寒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还记得北极熊的照片吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在它们周围我们看到了什么？”爸爸问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冰和水。”里基回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。北极太冷了，所以冰永远不会融化！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！那么，爸爸，我想立刻开始训练。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，需要你的帮助。”里基说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没问题。我怎么帮你？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你每个星期要多给我五美金的零用钱。”里基说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那样为什么能帮你训练？”爸爸问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有了那笔钱，”里基解释道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就可以买冰淇淋来适应严寒了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>